---
import MizuLayout from '@/layouts/MizuLayout.astro'
---

<MizuLayout
  title="Careers | Pixelated Empathy"
  description="Current hiring posture and future roles at Pixelated Empathy."
>
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="site-shell site-shell--narrow relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white"
        >
          Careers
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
          Pixelated Empathy is not running a broad hiring push right now. The
          company is still founder-led, and future roles will be added only
          where they directly improve the product and training workflow.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 mb-16">
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Clinical guidance</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Future collaborators should strengthen scenario quality, supervision
            workflows, and feedback language.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Product design</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            The product needs designers who can make sensitive, complicated
            workflows feel clear and usable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8"
        >
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
            Platform engineering
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Privacy, analytics, and reliable simulation infrastructure are the
            main technical hiring areas when roles open.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">No open roles today</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          If your background is unusually relevant to therapist training,
          privacy-aware AI systems, or clinical product design, you can still
          reach out. We would rather have a precise conversation than post a
          generic role description too early.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary-500/25 hover:shadow-primary-500/40 hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          Start a conversation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MizuLayout>
